Brickabulary 
App Support

🏆 About – What is Brickabulary?
Brickabulary is a fun Brick Breaker game designed to help players learn English vocabulary interactively. Break bricks to discover new words and test your knowledge through engaging mini-games!
📌 How to Play?
	•	Swipe to move the paddle and bounce the ball.
	•	Break bricks to reveal English words and their meanings.
	•	Complete each level and take mini vocabulary tests to reinforce learning!


📖 Frequently Asked Questions (FAQ)
📌 1️⃣ How do I play the game?
Swipe the paddle to keep the ball bouncing and break bricks to reveal new words.
📌 2️⃣ How are the words selected?
Words are randomly chosen based on your English proficiency level.
📌 3️⃣ How do I turn off the sound in the game?
You can disable sound effects and music from the game’s settings menu.
📌 4️⃣ The game is not working properly. What should I do?
If you experience any issues, please fill out the contact form below or email us directly.


